Foxfingers arrives at the Battle ground. Fallen trees, charred rock, 
burning bushes scattered the field. "To think this is why I left 
cybertron. Well this and a few outstanding depts." he thought as his 
hoverboard floated across the wasteland. "I must remember the reason 
I'm here." he paused as if to remind himself "Till all are one."

Foxfingers scanned the area and monitored the communications from the 
battle. The preds seemed pinned at the cave with the maximals moving 
in on all sides. The one called Deemos seemed to be the bot in charge 
it would have to be him that he contacted to open a raport with this 
group of maximals. He opened a comm "Deemos do you read me? My name 
is Foxfingers, are you in need of assistance?

--- In

make
